---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section
  class="py-20 lg:py-32 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12"
  id="about"
>
  <div class="flex-1 space-y-6 text-center lg:text-left">
    <div
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary border border-primary/20 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider"
    >
      <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
        <span
          class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-primary opacity-75"
        ></span>
        <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-primary"
        ></span>
      </span>
      Disponível para novos projetos
    </div>
    <h1
      class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white"
    >
      Desenvolvedor <span class="text-primary">Front-End</span>.
    </h1>
    <p
      class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 leading-relaxed"
    >
      Olá, sou Marcos. Sou um desenvolvedor Front-End focado em aplicações web,
      tenho usado ReactJs, mas já trabalhei com EmberJs, jQuery e front-ends
      dentro de Ruby On Rails. Meu foco é em código limpo e experiências de
      usuário excepcionais.
    </p>
    <!-- <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center lg:justify-start gap-4 pt-4">
      <button
        class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg font-bold transition-all flex items-center gap-2"
      >
        View Projects <Icon name="material-symbols:arrow-forward" size="24" />
      </button>
      <button
        class="bg-slate-200 dark:bg-neutral-dark hover:bg-slate-300 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg font-bold transition-all"
      >
        Contact Me
      </button>
    </div> -->
  </div>
  <div class="flex-1 flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
    <div class="relative w-64 h-64 lg:w-96 lg:h-96 w-56 h-56 lg:w-80 lg:h-80">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div
        class="relative w-full h-full rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border-4 border-white dark:border-neutral-border shadow-2xl hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500"
      >
        <img
          alt="Retrato profissional de Marcos Toledo"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          data-alt="Retrato profissional de um desenvolvedor sorrindo com os braços cruzados."
          src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/13186981?v=4"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
